^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Well we have lots to discuss on this hand. This is actually one of those rare hands where 5 of a minor is a better contract than 3N. Having said that, 3N should make (but on a different line of play). With the line of play Marge took, 3N could actually end up going down. First of all Marge, before we get into your line, why did you take your hearts first?|
