NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I notice that students like to duck Aces. There are certainly times when you should duck Aces. But you have to have a good reason such as cutting off an entry to declarer or dummy. However, most of the time you should not duck your Aces as long as they capture a high honor. If in doubt take your Ace as long as it captures a high honor from declarer.|
