^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let's talk about the bidding. Although a case can be made for opening 2C with Marge's hand, there is a good reason not to. Were Marge's long suit a major there is a much better case. However, particularly when your suit is diamonds, you should avoid opening 2C unless you have a really really strong hand. The reason for that is, the auction is likely to go 2C-2D-3D, and you are already at the 3 level with little information exchanged.|
